description:
There is actually nothing I don't like about this place, other than:

(1) it is not always open;
(2) one time I came here, there was a really long line; 
(3) another time I came here, it was super late in the day and they had run out of frozen yogurt, so I wasn't able to get the thing I wanted.

Tellingly, (1), (2), and (3) above all have to do with me not being able to here, or my eating here having been delayed or restricted in some way. These, I feel, are good problems to have.

The froyo is good. It is tasty and I like putting it in my mouth. The same is true of the rice pudding. Yum yum yum.
